    b"updated_after ISO 8601 timestamp strings.\x0a        - Use the current timestamp as"
    b" the reference point for recency.\x0a        - Choose each timestamp independently."
    b"\x0a        - Use older timestamps when older context may be useful.\x0a        - Use "
